    // Per-frame work is now: build a 1.7 KB RGB scratch buffer for each
    // active slot, hand it to the WebGL renderer (which diffs against its
    // own mirror and skips redundant texSubImage2D uploads), and submit
    // one drawArrays. The rAF body's expensive parts are the per-chapter
